items.name: Parks and Recreation Wiki
items.title: Parks and Recreation Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Parks and Recreation Wiki!
items.desc: Parks and Recreation Wiki is a collaborative project for the NBC television series Parks and Recreation. The mockumentary-syle show centers on Leslie Knope, a mid-level bureaucrat in the Parks and Recreation Department of Pawnee, Indiana and her colleagues. This wiki offers information on characters, episodes, the city of Pawnee, locations, and more.

items.name: Pimp My Gun Wiki
items.title: Pimp My Gun Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Pimp my Gun Wikia!
items.desc: Welcome to the Pimp My Gun Wikia, an entire wiki dedicated to the popular flash game, Pimp My Gun. Here you can post your custom guns, write about them, or look at other's creations. Pimp My Gun is an incredibly popular flash game that allows users to customize or create their own weapons using dozens of different parts, pieces, and accessories. Users and fans are encouraged to contribute!

items.name: Nation Creation Wiki
items.title: Nation Creation Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Nation Creation Wiki
items.desc:
The wiki devoted to NC & CYOC type games that anyone can edit.

Nation Creation is a free online game that allows you to create a simulated nation on Earth or in space. With open-ended gameplay, the possibilities for where you can take your future Empire are endless.

Create Your Own Country (CYOC), currently in its 39th edition, is the original game in the CYOC Genre.

items.name: Minecraft Creations Wiki
items.title: Minecraft Creations Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Minecraft Creations Wiki
items.desc: Minecraft is a game that leaves open endless possibilities for the player, and when players are given such freedom thier creativity comes alive. The goal of the Minecraft Creations Wiki is to provide a place where Minecraft players can come together and share the imaginative and purely amazing creations they have made. Become a member of our awesome community and share your creation today!

items.name: Creations Wiki
items.title: Creations Wiki
items.headline: The Wiki for any and all creations!
items.desc: The Creations wiki revolves around those who edit it, not a particular subject. Add your sculptures, drawings or any other creations you can think of! Because the size of the wiki depends on the contributors' creativity, the more users that join, the bigger the Wiki gets and the more variety there is in the art uploaded! However, be warned: we do not tolerate copying or stealing other users' creations.

items.title: Creation-Kit Wikia
items.desc: In diesem Wikia findest du Informationen rund um Bethesdas Creation Kit. Es soll vor allem deutschsprachigen Nutzern des Creation Kit dabei helfen, leichter in dessen Bedienung rein zu kommen. Es gibt im Internet bestimmt viele Möglichkeiten zu erfahren, wie man mit dem Creation Kit umgeht, aber leider sind dafür oft mehrere Suchvorgänge, sowie das kombinieren von Informationen mehrerer voneinander unabhängiger Seiten nötig oder man muss gut Englisch können, um zu verstehen was auf der Seite geschrieben steht.
